name: Star Wars The Force Awakens Alternate Please Stand By Movie Poster
description: Inspired by Tom Jung's original Star Wars Episode IV A New Hope Movie Poster, this new Force Awakens Poster takes the same theme and layout and adapts it for The Force Awakens.  Features a Signature Please Stand By Logo in the corner as well.  Everyone who buys one will be placed into a raffle for a 1/1 animated version of the poster.
